# 301 Redirects: Force all traffic to non-www HTTPS
# These rules execute BEFORE any other processing

# Force www to non-www with 301 (permanent redirect)
https://www.msylimoservice.com/* https://msylimoservice.com/:splat 301!
http://www.msylimoservice.com/* https://msylimoservice.com/:splat 301!

# Force HTTP to HTTPS
http://msylimoservice.com/* https://msylimoservice.com/:splat 301!

# SPA fallback - serve index.html for client-side routing
/*    /index.html   200
